\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1340632 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10756693\charrsid9666090 They eat all the middle out of it.
