\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1340632 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10756693\charrsid9666090 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6641509 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10756693\charrsid9666090 Did she ever talk about the times it was open - what hours it was open?
