\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6641509 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10756693\charrsid9666090 From what time in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1340632 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10756693\charrsid9666090 And I've heard her say that they used to clean their shop step after that so that it was all clean and tidy for the next morning.
