nd when it came to spring cleaning when I used to lift this picture down I used to say by golly he was a big heavy fellow when he was alive he's still heavier now. And of course he was a dogmatic kind of a granddad - he - he was - on all accounts he was a
 driver you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6641509 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10756693\charrsid9666090 You mean drove himself hard manually?
