he'd practice on the piano, you see, and grandfather'd say, come along, come along, work to be done, kind of thing. Well, this cousin eventually became the organist at St Francis Monastery at Gorton. He was there for - oh - I should think twenty years or 
more. And - his name was Sharples too. We - he was one of mother's brother's boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6641509 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10756693\charrsid9666090 Did your mother work after she had children?
