m on the couch - sort of recuperating - and there was a gentleman visitor came to the house and mother showed him in and as she came through the door she said 'get up off that couch and sit down, it's not discreet of you to be laying there on'. Just becau
se I was - resting I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6641509 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10756693\charrsid9666090 What about how you sat on a chair?
