t girls who's the youngest of the family - she's left behind and that was it. But at one time I wanted to be a nurse and - mother approached the doctor and the doctor said well it was a very hard life and - very - not very nice to be - you now, some unple
asant things. Yes, unpleasant jobs they had to do and this that and the other. So of course I was talked out of that.
